OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBrighter spells likely at
OL,6,Ffirst, and soon feeling warm in any
OL,7,Fsunshine. Cloud then thickens late
OL,8,Fmorning, with outbreaks of rain during
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Turning colder, breezy
OL,10,Fwith occasional showers later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with occasional
OL,13,Fshowers at first becoming more settled
OL,14,Fovernight and partly cloudy at times,
OL,15,Fwith easing winds and feeling cooler
OL,16,Fwith mist and fog patches possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
