OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FChilly start Friday then sunny
OL,6,Fintervals, cloud thickening later with
OL,7,Fa band of rain spreading eastwards
OL,8,Fthrough the region. the wind will
OL,9,Fgradually increase overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,12,Fand strong winds early Saturday,
OL,13,Ffollowed by sunshine and blustery
OL,14,Fshowers into Sunday. Feeling rather
OL,15,Fcool at times. Monday blustery showers
OL,16,Fwill gradually ease through the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
